Até breve, Hank.

1447
01:44:36,618 --> 01:44:38,036
Sinceramente, Hope...

1448
01:44:38,911 --> 01:44:40,330
-Scott.
-Sim?

1449
01:44:40,580 --> 01:44:42,707
